item.title: South Korea protesters rally for, against Yoon arrest as deadline looms
item.description: Yoon became the country's first sitting president to face arrest over his botched attempt to declare martial law on Dec. 3.

item.title: Austrian chancellor quits as coalition talks collapse
item.description: Talks between Austria's two main centrist parties on forming a coalition government without the far-right Freedom Party collapsed on Saturday.
